appendObjects in the adapter:

        public void appendObjects (List&lt;MyObj&gt; obj)
        {
            foreach (var o in obj) {
                data.Add (o);
            }
        }

appendObject in kotlin

    fun appendObjects(obj: List&lt;MyObj&gt;) {
        obj.forEach { 
            data.Add (it); 
        } 
    }

